## For the First Prototype - 

# Electronics

Board - Node MCU esp32 version
ecg module - ad8232 single channel 1 lead ecg version
Pulse sensor - from pulsesensor.com
Temperature sensor - DS18B20 with probe
lipo charger circuit

# Medical
Ecg electrodes - Self made electrodes from a conductive silver fabric coated with polyamide material
needs to be dipped into pedot:pss solution

